stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> available

    available --> assistance_requested : wave detected
    assistance_requested --> assistance_in_progress : staff acknowledge
    assistance_in_progress --> available : staff resolve

    available --> offline : device disconnects
    assistance_requested --> offline : device disconnects
    assistance_in_progress --> offline : device disconnects
    offline --> available : device reconnects

    available --> error : runtime or inference failure
    assistance_requested --> error : runtime or inference failure
    assistance_in_progress --> error : runtime or inference failure
    error --> available : reset or recovery

    available --> training_ready : enter training mode
    training_ready --> training_positive : capture positive sample
    training_ready --> training_negative : capture negative sample
    training_positive --> training_ready : next sample
    training_negative --> training_ready : next sample
    training_ready --> available : exit training mode
